ω\">ἐποίησαν</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>·<span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">Θ</span>·<span data-text=\"Καταχθονίοις\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">Κ</span>·<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κασσία Βενοῦστα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κασσία\"><span data-text=\"Κασσία\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Κασσία\">ΚΑΣΣΙΑ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βενοῦστα\"><span data-text=\"Βενοῦστα\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Βενοῦστα\">ΒΕΝΟΥΣΤΑ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἔ\n                    ζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">Ε<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span>·<span data-text=\"ἔνδεκα\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ἔνδεκα\">ΕΝΔΕΚΑ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"μῆνες\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">Μ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Η͡Ν͡Ε</span>Σ</span>·<span data-text=\"θ\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"θ\">Θ</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρες\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΕΣ</span>·<span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"η\">Η</span>·<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"πατὴρ\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"πατήρ\">ΠΑ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>Ρ</span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"καί\">ΚΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"μήτηρ\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"μήτηρ\">ΜΗ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>Ρ</span><span data-text=\"τέ ·\n                    κνῳ\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"τέκνον\">ΤΕ- ·<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΚΝΩ</span><span data-text=\"γλυκυτάτῳ\" data-n=\"120\" data-lemma=\"γλυκύς\">ΓΛΥΚΥΤΑΤΩ</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησαν\" data-n=\"125\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΑΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">ΘΕΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Καταχθονίοις\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">ΚΑΤΑΧΘΟΝΙΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Κασσία\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Κασσία\">ΚΑΣΣΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"Βενοῦστα\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Βενοῦστα\">ΒΕΝΟΥΣΤΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ἔνδεκα\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ἔνδεκα\">ΕΝΔΕΚΑ</span><span data-text=\"μῆνες\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΕΣ</span><span data-text=\"θ\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"θ\">Θ</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρες\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΕΣ</span><span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"η\">Η</span><span data-text=\"πατὴρ\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"πατήρ\">ΠΑΤΗΡ</span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"καί\">ΚΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"μήτηρ\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"μήτηρ\">ΜΗΤΗΡ</span><span data-text=\"τέκνῳ\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"τέκνον\">ΤΕΚΝΩ</span><span data-text=\"γλυκυτάτῳ\" data-n=\"120\" data-lemma=\"γλυκύς\">ΓΛΥΚΥΤΑΤΩ</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησαν\" data-n=\"125\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΑΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001306_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001306_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001306.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001306-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based on photographs</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"line 5\">line.5: <span>Kaibel saw an ivy leaf at the end of the line, but it rather seems to be a triangle-shaped interpunct.</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>To the underworld spirits. Kassia Benousta, lived for 11 years, 9 months, and 8 days. Her father and mother made this for their sweetest child.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>Agli Dei inferi. Kassia Benousta visse 11 anni, 9 mesi e 8 giorni. Suo padre e sua madre realizzarono questo per la loro dolce figlia.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The structure of the epitaph is the most frequent in pagan epitaphs, with the invocation to the underworld spirits, the name of the deceased in the nominative form, his/her age, the name of the dedicants (in this case, the parents) and the dedication verb in aorist (Korhonen 2004: 85-86). An interesting linguistic detail is the indication of months and days in the nominative and not in the accusative form (<span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">μῆνες, ἡμέρες</span>), which seems to be due to confusion with Latin where the nominative and accusative plural of <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">mensis</span> and <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">dies</span> correspond: for a similar confusion, see also SEG 44.0762 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000641\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000641</a>. On the name <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Βενοῦστα</span>, see SEG 29.931-3 (from Morgantina, 1st century CE). Note too the spelling out of the first numeral in full, rather than using the standard alphabetic notation.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li></li><li> Spuches 1864 13 no.3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002042\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002042</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">483</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 67 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li> Korhonen 2004 85-86 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Regular letters: rhomboid Θ, Ο, Ω (open); Α with accentuated upper serif, Μ with slanting full-length bars (but irregular), Υ with an extended right arm (line 6), ΗΝΕ at l. 4 and ΤΗ at l. 5 (x2) in ligature. In the last line, some letters are smaller than others for lack of space.</p> Lines 1-6  20-25  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not registered  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
